{"type": "article", "id": 2708, "title": "Paul Smith彩色咖啡壶", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-08T07:43:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232449DaNZbplhEvrF5s6W.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国设计师 Paul Smith 在鲜艳色彩与传统细腻上的拿捏尺度，总是令人拍案叫绝。在丹麦设计品牌 Stelton 的50 周年庆典上，Paul Smith 再度发挥其朝气蓬勃的创作功力，重新诠释了已故丹麦设计师 Arne Jacobsen 在 1960 年代设计的 Cylinda 咖啡壶，不锈钢材质使其整体看上去更具质感，而壶把则选用了 Paul Smith 特有的着色手段进行点缀，使产品整体看上去更加灵动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232447QJOFHqlLA0Itis4E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232448wC5SLBb0HuvUO7nQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232448euOwxDQTVnzqAUM6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.021875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}